		"inclusion": "Activate the inclusion mode (teach-in mode) on the gateway. (for further details please refer to the gateways manual)Press the \"+\" key (Add / Inclusion) in your Z-Wave app and follow the instructions to set the gateway to Inclusion mode.Keep the device within range of the gateway.Remove the fuse strip from the battery compartment. The device supports automatic inclusion, i.e. it automatically goes into inclusion mode when it is powered and not yet connected to a gateway. Alternative Inclusion:If the security strip has already been removed, instead press the Link button 3 times quickly (within 1.5 seconds) to start the inclusion on the device.",
